# 💬 WhatsApp Chat Analyzer

A Python-based interactive web application that analyzes exported WhatsApp chats and generates meaningful insights through statistics and visualizations. Built using Streamlit, Pandas, Matplotlib, and Seaborn.

---

## Features

### Chat Statistics
- Total Messages
- Total Words
- Media Shared
- Links Shared

### Timeline Analysis
- Monthly activity timeline
- Daily activity timeline

### User Analysis
- Individual user statistics
- Group statistics
- Most active users

### Activity Analysis
- Weekly activity distribution
- Monthly activity distribution
- Hourly activity heatmap

### Text Analysis
- Word Cloud
- Most Common Words
- Emoji Usage Analysis

---

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- WordCloud
- URLExtract
- Emoji
- Regular Expressions (Regex)

